  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Weight loss within the past 4 weeks

          -  Infants 1-12 months of age feeding a hypoallergenic formula for at least 2 weeks

          -  Birth weight greater than or equal to 1500 grams

          -  Solely enteral fed

          -  Infants with at least one persistent allergy symptom

          -  No change in medication within 10 days of beginning the study and no plans for change
             during the first 10 days of the study

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of underlying condition which, in the Investigator's opinion, could interfere
             with normal growth, development, or assessment of the participant

          -  Metabolic disease requiring special attention
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
